OL,4,BAston Villa pair Wesley and Tom Heaton
OL,5,Bout for season with knee injuries
OL,6, Aston Villa will be without striker
OL,7, Wesley and goalkeeper Tom Heaton for
OL,8, the rest of the season after both
OL,9, suffered knee ligament damage in
OL,10, Wednesday's 2-1 win at Burnley. 
OL,12,FBrazil international Wesley, 23, scored
OL,13,Fthe opener but was hurt in a tackle
OL,14,Fwith Clarets' defender Ben Mee. 
OL,16,FFormer Burnley keeper Heaton, 33, was
OL,17,Fhurt as he attempted to stop Chris Wood
OL,18,F80th-minute consolation.
OL,20,FBoth players had scans on Thursday and
OL,21,Fare set for six to nine months out.
